<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>【2025年9月最新版】最強双剣ランキング | モンハンNow</title>
  <meta name="description" content="モンハンNowの最強双剣ランキングを、おすすめ装備構成つきで属性別に徹底解説。火・雷・龍・氷・水・無属性・爆破・睡眠まで、実データ入りで見やすくまとめた特集ページです。" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#07090d;
      --bg-soft:#0c1017;
      --panel:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
      --panel-strong:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      --line:rgba(255,255,255,.09);
      --text:#f5f7fb;
      --muted:#aeb6c7;
      --gold:#d8b775;
      --gold-soft:rgba(216,183,117,.15);
      --blue:#89a9ff;
      --danger:#ef7575;
      --shadow:0 22px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.42);
      --radius:28px;
      --radius-sm:18px;
      --max:1240px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      font-family:"Inter","Noto Sans JP",sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 0%, rgba(216,183,117,.15), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 5%, rgba(137,169,255,.10), transparent 25%),
        linear-gradient(180deg,#06070b 0%, #0b1017 46%, #07090d 100%);
      line-height:1.75;
      -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
      text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
    }

    a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    img{display:block;width:100%}
    .container{width:min(var(--max), calc(100% - 28px)); margin-inline:auto}

    .topbar{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:9999;
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      background:rgba(7,9,13,.7);
      backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
    }
    .topbar-inner{
      width:min(var(--max), calc(100% - 28px));
      margin:auto;
      min-height:72px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:18px;
    }
    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
    }
    .brand-mark{
      width:38px;
      height:38px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #fff3ce);
      box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(216,183,117,.35);
      flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .brand small{
      display:block;
      font-size:11px;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .brand strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:14px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
    }
    .nav{
      display:flex;
      gap:16px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    .nav a{
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:.12em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
      transition:.25s;
    }
    .nav a:hover{color:#fff}

    .hero{
      padding:54px 0 34px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .hero-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;
      gap:20px;
      align-items:stretch;
    }
    .hero-copy,
    .hero-visual{
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:34px;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,255,255,.03));
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      position:relative;
    }
    .hero-copy{
      padding:34px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:center;
      min-height:560px;
    }
    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      width:max-content;
      padding:8px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#f7e0a8;
      background:var(--gold-soft);
      border:1px solid rgba(216,183,117,.26);
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }
    .hero h1{
      font-size:clamp(30px, 5vw, 62px);
      line-height:1.05;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      font-weight:800;
    }
    .hero-lead{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:15px;
      max-width:60ch;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }
    .meta-row{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }
    .chip{
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      color:#dde3ee;
      font-size:13px;
    }
    .hero-actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:12px;
    }
    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      min-height:48px;
      padding:0 18px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:14px;
      font-weight:700;
      transition:.25s ease;
      border:1px solid transparent;
    }
    .btn-primary{
      color:#101114;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #f3ddb0);
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(216,183,117,.22);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
    .btn-ghost{
      color:#fff;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}

    .hero-visual{
      min-height:560px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,.08), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg,#151922 0%, #0c1017 100%);
    }
    .hero-pattern{
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,183,117,.12), transparent 34%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 18%, rgba(137,169,255,.12), transparent 20%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .hero-panel{
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto 24px 24px 24px;
      background:rgba(10,12,18,.72);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:22px;
    }
    .hero-panel h2{
      font-size:18px;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }
    .hero-panel p{
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--muted);
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }
    .hero-panel ul{
      list-style:none;
      display:grid;
      gap:8px;
    }
    .hero-panel li{
      font-size:13px;
      color:#e4e9f3;
      padding-left:14px;
      position:relative;
    }
    .hero-panel li::before{
      content:"";
      width:5px;
      height:5px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background:var(--gold);
      position:absolute;
      left:0;
      top:.7em;
    }

    .stats{
      padding:10px 0 26px;
    }
    .stats-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
      gap:14px;
    }
    .stat-card{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:20px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }
    .stat-card small{
      display:block;
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:.12em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }
    .stat-card strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:30px;
      line-height:1.1;
      margin-bottom:6px;
    }
    .stat-card span{
      font-size:13px;
      color:#d9dfeb;
    }

    .section{
      padding:28px 0;
    }
    .section-head{
      display:flex;
      align-items:end;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:18px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }
    .section-head h2{
      font-size:clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px);
      line-height:1.08;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }
    .section-head p{
      max-width:62ch;
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .summary-wrap{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr .95fr;
      gap:18px;
    }
    .summary-card,
    .toc-card{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border-radius:26px;
      padding:24px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }
    .summary-card h3,
    .toc-card h3{
      font-size:21px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }
    .summary-list{
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
      list-style:none;
    }
    .summary-list li{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:12px;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      font-size:14px;
    }
    .summary-list strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:15px;
    }
    .summary-list span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:13px;
    }

    .toc-links{
      display:grid;
      gap:10px;
      list-style:none;
    }
    .toc-links a{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:14px;
      padding:13px 15px;
      border-radius:18px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      transition:.2s ease;
      font-size:14px;
    }
    .toc-links a:hover{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      transform:translateX(4px);
    }

    .weapon-section{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,255,255,.03));
      border-radius:32px;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }
    .weapon-head{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;
      min-height:320px;
    }
    .weapon-copy{
      padding:30px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:center;
    }
    .weapon-kicker{
      color:#f1d79f;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }
    .weapon-copy h3{
      font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,42px);
      line-height:1.08;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }
    .weapon-desc{
      font-size:15px;
      color:var(--muted);
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }
    .weapon-tags{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }
    .weapon-tags span{
      font-size:12px;
      padding:9px 11px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      color:#e5ebf6;
    }
    .weapon-note{
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      border:1px solid rgba(216,183,117,.16);
      background:rgba(216,183,117,.09);
      color:#f4f6fb;
      font-size:14px;
    }
    .weapon-visual{
      position:relative;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.02), rgba(0,0,0,.12)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 75% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,.08), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #161b24 0%, #0c1017 100%);
      min-height:320px;
    }
    .weapon-visual::before{
      content:attr(data-label);
      position:absolute;
      right:22px;
      bottom:18px;
      font-size:48px;
      line-height:1;
      font-weight:800;
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      letter-spacing:.04em;
    }
    .weapon-visual-inner{
      position:absolute;
      inset:22px;
      border-radius:24px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,183,117,.12), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.02));
      display:flex;
      align-items:end;
      padding:24px;
    }
    .weapon-visual-card{
      max-width:340px;
      border-radius:20px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(9,11,17,.74);
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      padding:18px;
    }
    .weapon-visual-card strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      font-size:18px;
    }
    .weapon-visual-card p{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .build-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:18px;
      padding:0 30px 30px;
    }
    .build-card{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:22px;
    }
    .build-card h4{
      font-size:17px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }
    .equip-list{
      list-style:none;
      display:grid;
      gap:10px;
    }
    .equip-list li{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      padding-bottom:10px;
      border-bottom:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color:#e3e8f3;
      font-size:14px;
    }
    .equip-list li:last-child{
      border-bottom:none;
      padding-bottom:0;
    }
    .label{
      min-width:44px;
      color:#f1d79f;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .mini-section{
      margin-top:14px;
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }
    .mini-section strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      font-size:14px;
    }
    .mini-section p{
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .related{
      padding:8px 0 72px;
    }
    .related-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:18px;
    }
    .related-card{
      min-height:220px;
      border-radius:24px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.02)),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,183,117,.12), transparent 32%),
        #0d121a;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      padding:24px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:flex-end;
    }
    .related-card small{
      display:block;
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
      letter-spacing:.12em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }
    .related-card h4{
      font-size:22px;
      line-height:1.22;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }
    .related-card p{
      font-size:14px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .footer{
      padding:0 0 34px;
      text-align:center;
      color:#97a0b0;
      font-size:13px;
    }

    .fade-up{
      opacity:0;
      transform:translateY(28px);
      transition:opacity .75s ease, transform .75s ease;
    }
    .fade-up.show{
      opacity:1;
      transform:none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px){
      .hero-grid,
      .summary-wrap,
      .weapon-head,
      .build-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .stats-grid,
      .related-grid{
        grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
      }
      .hero-copy,
      .hero-visual{
        min-height:auto;
      }
      .hero-visual{
        min-height:420px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .topbar-inner{
        padding:14px 0;
        align-items:flex-start;
        min-height:auto;
        flex-direction:column;
      }
      .nav{
        gap:10px 14px;
      }
      .hero{
        padding-top:34px;
      }
      .hero-copy,
      .summary-card,
      .toc-card,
      .stat-card,
      .build-card{
        padding:20px;
      }
      .stats-grid,
      .related-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .weapon-copy{
        padding:22px;
      }
      .build-grid{
        padding:0 22px 22px;
      }
      .weapon-visual{
        min-height:260px;
      }
      .weapon-visual::before{
        font-size:36px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <a href="#" class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark"></div>
        <div>
          <small>Monster Hunter Now</small>
          <strong>Dual Blades Special Feature</strong>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#summary">Summary</a>
        <a href="#contents">Contents</a>
        <a href="#fire">Fire</a>
        <a href="#thunder">Thunder</a>
        <a href="#dragon">Dragon</a>
        <a href="#ice">Ice</a>
        <a href="#water">Water</a>
        <a href="#raw">Raw</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy fade-up">
          <div class="eyebrow">2025 September Update</div>
          <h1>最強双剣ランキングを、<br>“読まれる記事”から<br>“魅せる特集ページ”へ。</h1>
          <p class="hero-lead">
            モンハンNowの双剣を、火・雷・龍・氷・水・無属性・爆破・睡眠まで属性別に整理。
            ただのブログ記事ではなく、結論の見やすさ・滞在時間・回遊率まで意識した構成で、
            実データ入りの特集ページとしてそのまま組み込める形に再構築しています。
          </p>

          <div class="meta-row">
            <div class="chip">最終更新：2025.09.30</div>
            <div class="chip">双剣ランキング特集</div>
            <div class="chip">装備構成あり</div>
            <div class="chip">スマホ最適化済み</div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#summary">結論から見る</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#contents">目次へ</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual fade-up">
          <div class="hero-pattern"></div>
          <div class="hero-panel">
            <h2>このページの見どころ</h2>
            <p>元記事の実データをもとに、ランキング性と高級感を両立するよう再設計。</p>
            <ul>
              <li>火・雷・龍・氷・水・無属性・爆破・睡眠の8カテゴリ対応</li>
              <li>おすすめ装備構成をカードUIで視認性アップ</li>
              <li>スマホでも一瞬で要点が伝わる比較重視レイアウト</li>
              <li>関連記事導線を追加し、回遊しやすい構造に最適化</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
      <div class="container stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card fade-up">
          <small>Categories</small>
          <strong>8</strong>
          <span>属性・状態異常ごとに整理</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card fade-up">
          <small>Builds</small>
          <strong>10+</strong>
          <span>構成データを見やすく掲載</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card fade-up">
          <small>Updated</small>
          <strong>09.30</strong>
          <span>更新感の見せ方も強化</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card fade-up">
          <small>Mobile</small>
          <strong>100%</strong>
          <span>縦スクロールで映える設計</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="summary">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head fade-up">
          <div>
            <h2>まず結論だけ見たい人向け</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            先に注目武器を見せることで、検索から来たユーザーの離脱を減らしやすくなります。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-wrap">
          <div class="summary-card fade-up">
            <h3>注目の双剣まとめ</h3>
            <ul class="summary-list">
              <li>
                <div>
                  <strong>火属性：ゲキリュウノツガイ</strong>
                  <span>会心率30％＋会心撃〖属性〗構成で高火力</span>
                </div>
                <div>S</div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div>
                  <strong>雷属性：迅雷・トルネ＝ジャナール</strong>
                  <span>コスパ・流用・火力のバランスが優秀</span>
                </div>
                <div>S</div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div>
                  <strong>龍属性：死罪〖デスロウ〗</strong>
                  <span>待望の龍属性会心武器として個性も強い</span>
                </div>
                <div>A+</div>
              </li>
              <li>
